snippet.textDisplay:
The Good Lord whatever name you call Him by has given us 2 eyes & ears but one heart & head to realize the beautiful Oneness of the World. That all of Life is ONE family that dwells by the Divine Grace of God. Nobody, No nation has thrived or will ever know peace by killing one of its kind. Nations are a NOTION. Entrust yourself to God to discover the blissful realization that the Universal Essence of Love is worshiped as Allah Hu/Hari Om.

The Essence of Maula & Mauli is ONE. Every Khud is an integral part of One Khuda. _/\_ 
Only Pure Love for the Lord that will enable ALL of Humanity to live in Peace & Harmony.
